This proof is quite straightforward because the exhaustive condition is preserved in the child derivations due to the way context-free derivations are structured. The automation in Lean (`simp_all`, `aesop`) helps in deducing the necessary implications without having to manually check each case. The actual work is done by the definitions and the logical structure of the problem, while Lean's automation handles the details of the proof search. 

